# FLIP BOARD MESSAGES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Messages displayed on the flip board. Rotates every 6 seconds.
# Use \n for line breaks within each message.
NEXT_PUBLIC_BOARD_MSG_1="STAY HUNGRY \nSTAY IN BED \n- STEVE JOBS"
