# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CHAT GREETINGS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
NEXT_PUBLIC_GREETING_1="Hi there! I'm an AI agent trained on docs, help articles, and other important content."
NEXT_PUBLIC_GREETING_2="How can I best help you today?"

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# FAQ ACCORDION
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Questions and answers shown in the accordion on the landing page.
NEXT_PUBLIC_FAQ_1_TITLE="How do I place an order?"
NEXT_PUBLIC_FAQ_1_CONTENT="Browse our products, add items to your cart, and proceed to checkout. You'll need to provide shipping and payment information to complete your purchase."

NEXT_PUBLIC_FAQ_2_TITLE="Can I modify or cancel my order?"
NEXT_PUBLIC_FAQ_2_CONTENT="Yes, you can modify or cancel your order before it's shipped. Once your order is processed, you can't make changes."

NEXT_PUBLIC_FAQ_3_TITLE="What payment methods do you accept?"
NEXT_PUBLIC_FAQ_3_CONTENT="We accept all major credit cards, debit cards, and PayPal. Your payment information is encrypted and processed securely."

NEXT_PUBLIC_FAQ_4_TITLE="How long does shipping take?"
NEXT_PUBLIC_FAQ_4_CONTENT="Standard shipping typically takes 5-7 business days. Express shipping is available for 2-3 business day delivery."

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CHAT WIDGET SUGGESTION BUTTONS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Label = button text, Prompt = message sent when clicked.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUGGEST_1_LABEL="Get started"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUGGEST_1_PROMPT="How do I get started with the platform?"

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUGGEST_2_LABEL="See templates"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUGGEST_2_PROMPT="Can you show me the available templates?"

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUGGEST_3_LABEL="Pricing"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUGGEST_3_PROMPT="What are the pricing plans available?"

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUGGEST_4_LABEL="Book a demo"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUGGEST_4_PROMPT="I would like to book a demo."

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUGGEST_5_LABEL="Documentation"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUGGEST_5_PROMPT="Where can I find the API documentation?"
